<section class="hero">
  <h1 class="ssh-command">
    <a href="/auth">ssh exe.dev <span class="cursor">_</span></a>
  </h1>
  <p class="tagline">The disk persists. You have sudo.</p>
  <p class="explanation">Persistent VMs via SSH. Start coding in seconds.</p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 36rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .ssh-command {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ssh-command a {
    transition: text-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .ssh-command a:hover {
    text-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.5),
      0 0 40px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.25),
      0 0 60px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .cursor {
    animation: blink 1s infinite;
  }

  .tagline {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .explanation {
    color: var(--color-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-btn-bg);
    color: var(--color-btn-text);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-btn-hover);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ssh-command {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .explanation {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .ssh-command {
      font-size: 3.75rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
